原内容: :【国安主题！北京这家麦当劳“绿了”】A McDonald’s in Beijing is about to subvert your color-scheme expectations. One of them has its exteriors painted completely green in support of Guoan, a Beijing-based football club. The restaurant is located at Donsi Shitiao, close to the club’s home stadium. Posters supporting the team are plastered all inside. According to The Mirror, a Beijing-based newspaper, the McDonald’s is going to fund training equipment for the club’s young footballers this year. The green restaurant, along with two others being refurbished, is intended to promote the sport. #国安# #麦当劳# #中国足球# #足球#
